Package: rk3588-codec-udev
Version: 1.0
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Yi Ding <yi.s.ding@gmail.com>
Description: udev rules for RK3588 hardware video codec + RGA device access
 Grants the "video" group read/write access to /dev/mpp_service (Rockchip MPP
 H.264/H.265 encoder + H.264/H.265/VP9 decoder) and /dev/rga (RGA 2D
 accelerator), so ffmpeg-rockchip / Jellyfin can use the hardware without root.
 Users (e.g. the jellyfin service account) must be in the "video" group.
